Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 姐姐为什么坐在香川的车上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:45.83,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:51.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:57.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:03.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:10.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:15.73,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:18.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.23,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:42.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.23,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.25,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:45.83,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:51.73,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:57.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:03.60,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:10.73,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:15.73,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:21.99,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:30.23,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.21,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:42.40,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:47.23,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.25,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的那天 我和姐姐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没来电话也没短信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以姐姐从早上就不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就总看手机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 他恰巧路过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香川 姐姐的前男友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总打姐姐的差劲男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年下男友怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着那小子 矢野？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好的天儿 把你撂下了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七月二十九 姐姐的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以姐姐才一早就等着手机响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 等下等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句生日快乐就上车了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来句圣诞快乐就跟着回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来句我喜欢你重新开始吧就直接上旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无药可救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧道歉就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 下午
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我检查了遗物里姐姐的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用短信 重要的事要亲口传达啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不巧没人接听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来电话时是下午四点十五
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是姐姐和香川兜风那会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐出事是下午四点三十八
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐为什么不接你电话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂什么现在和矢野说这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的事为什么现在才说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说些让矢野混乱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学你到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啊 没什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就没什么 放心地回去吧 高桥同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事 和高桥同学你没任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么目的 复仇 找讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙上车要怪我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去葬礼是我冷酷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为生日没在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么那时不接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香川在一起就没法接？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说法对死去的人好过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪过不会因为死了就变轻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我开始交往后 她到底没和香川结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你的罪过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的 罪过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的那天的事 已经忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快些妈妈就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只黑猫 小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是周五吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑猫是从眼前穿过时不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你刚才怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是第一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次啊 害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那样回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就没忘记姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你同时背叛我和姐姐两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你把我当成姐姐的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都和你想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来减轻你的罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐手机的通话记录里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多是香川打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是那天 好像整个夏天都在联系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先背叛的是对方 真好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啊 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一生也不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼啊 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到书包角了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然就扔东西啊 流血啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 高桥 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我是局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事儿瞒着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么瞒着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说没有隐瞒的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不要背叛又背叛的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 你说我背叛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你吧 所谓背叛是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍重 蹂躏 弄成七零八落破乱不堪再抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多么珍重你 难道你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我多想和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候背叛过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候抛弃过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候抛弃过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野觉得被奈奈抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓背叛是说不珍重 蹂躏 弄成七零八落破乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野说出那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一生也不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要接近矢野的心 光是喜欢还不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的喜欢不能化作矢野的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望他信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 我都接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别做告诉高桥那样的傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真话呀 你会后悔一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会说啊 怎么会说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还是那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方就是山本那种话 就这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你后悔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔？ 我自己做的事无论什么都不会后悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没后悔过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 为什么隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的哭脸 我不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会哭啊 肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是后悔 不是后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是感觉 有些失态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 好难搭话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天想着今天和他说话 都已经中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 我们去打躲避球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我得写日志 就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}值日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事好像假的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野和山本同学在班里像不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 英语书忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了?课本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话 第五节课就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 今天你回答问题 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 没有书做不了作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真是惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我想起你回答问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚全翻译好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都注释好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄到两点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 还是恨不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 却这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 全世界最喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你 才讨厌你骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是明白我的话 就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 我都接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三选一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 我向山本告白后被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 山本向我告白后被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 我和山本两情相悦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 是哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才是热身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 我对山本性骚扰过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 山本同学尾行过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 才到一半啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你总是那样打岔 一开始就没想认真讲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 第三个可能最怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 我跟山本做过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的净是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你想出那种过分的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是玩笑也好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 我都接受
